       IDENTIFICATION   DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.      prog.
       AUTHOR. tester.
       DATA             DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE  SECTION.
       PROCEDURE        DIVISION.
           STOP RUN.
])

